  chinamobile_name: "China Mobile (中国移动)",
  chinamobile_desc: "China Mobile is the official Mini Program by China Mobile Communications Group. It provides mobile users with real-time data and balance inquiry, recharge services, usage breakdown, and account management. Users can log in with their mobile number and access personalized dashboards and WeChat-integrated payments.",
  chinaunicom_name: "China Unicom (中国联通)",
  chinaunicom_desc: "China Unicom’s WeChat Mini Program provides mobile service management, bill payments, data packages, and customer support. Users can check usage, recharge accounts, and access telecom services conveniently from their phone.",
  fudanecard_name: "Fudan eCard",
  fudanecard_desc: "Fudan eCard (复旦一卡通) is the official campus card Mini Program for Fudan University. It supports virtual card payments, identity verification, meal ordering, water control, dorm access, and real-time account management. Students and staff can recharge, report lost cards, and view transaction history—all through unified identity authentication.",
  fudanalumnicard_name: "Fudan Alumni Card (复旦校友卡)",
  fudanalumnicard_desc: "Developed by Fudan University’s Alumni Association and IT Office, this Mini Program enables alumni to verify their identity, access campus services, and enjoy exclusive benefits. Features include campus entry via QR code, dining access, library reservations, and future perks in travel, finance, and shopping.",
  bosszhipin_name: "BOSS Zhipin (BOSS直聘)",
  bosszhipin_desc: "BOSS Zhipin is a direct-chat recruitment Mini Program that connects job seekers with hiring managers in real time. Users can browse openings, filter by location and role, and initiate conversations instantly—without intermediaries. The platform uses intelligent matching to recommend jobs based on resume and preferences.",
  yupaozhipin_name: "Yupao Zhipin (鱼泡直聘)",
  yupaozhipin_desc: "Yupao Zhipin is a recruitment platform focused on blue-collar and frontline jobs, spanning construction, logistics, manufacturing, and more. It supports instant messaging and direct calls to help job seekers connect quickly with employers.",
